title: Warriors down Hornets, advance to play Tioga
text:
Warriors down Hornets, advance to play Tioga 
By wbng sports October 25, 2015 Updated Oct 25, 2015 at 12:00 AM EDT 
Walton, NY (WBNG Binghamton) A tipped ball fell into the arms of Jordan Somers late in the first half and Walton (7-1) never looked back from its 22-6 halftime lead. The Warriors beat Harpursville/Afton (6-2), 36-18, Saturday in the Class D sectional quarterfinals. 
The win was Walton's first postseason victory since 2011. 
The Warriors advance to play Tioga (7-1) in the Class D semifinals on Saturday, Oct. 31 at 12:00 p.m. at Alumni Stadium in Binghamton. 
The schools have not met since 2012; Tioga has won the last two matchups.
